<h1>Biking across Canada</h1>
<h3>From Vancouver to St John's</h3>

<center>
<p align="justify">
Hello and welcome to my website describing my journey across Canada on my bicycle. I have three goals for this website. My first goal is to inspire those who are curious about touring to partake in a bike tour adventure. My second goal is to provide information and insights for those already planning a trip - I hope I will leave you with the impression that it's not that hard to plan (just get your gear and go). My third goal is to document and remember my travels.</p>



